STRUCTR.title: Structural Imbalance
STRUCTR.summary: Responsibilities bleed across modules or classes, pointing to poor separation of concerns.

TECHDEBT.title: Technical Debt
TECHDEBT.summary: Indicators show accruing debt that will require refactoring to sustain velocity.

CMPLX.title: Complexity Hotspot
CMPLX.summary: Cyclomatic or cognitive complexity exceeds recommended bounds, increasing maintenance risk.

COGNIT.title: Cognitive Overload
COGNIT.summary: Nested control flow and branching overload short-term memory, making the code hard to follow.

MAINTAIN.title: Maintainability Drift
MAINTAIN.summary: Signals reveal code that resists change or lacks clear ownership.

REFACTR.title: Refactoring Opportunity
REFACTR.summary: General refactoring signals indicate room for improvement.

XTRCLS.title: Extract Class
XTRCLS.summary: Split multi-purpose modules into cohesive components.

RDCOGN.title: Reduce Cognitive
RDCOGN.summary: Streamline control flow to ease human comprehension.

REFQLTY.title: Refactor Code Quality
REFQLTY.summary: Invest in broad cleanups to stabilize quality drift.

RDCYCLEX.title: Reduce Cyclomatic
RDCYCLEX.summary: Break apart dense branching to keep cyclomatic complexity in check.
